Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:02.55,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Takeshi and I had dinner together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:06.85,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Since I hadn't seen him in ages, I talked so much he could barely get a word in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.49,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,He was surprised, to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:16.68,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,In the end, Takeshi couldn't get any time off for work for Golden Week, so I didn't get to see him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:23.87,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I planned on sulking for a while, but I was so happy to see Takeshi's face that I got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:28.88,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,But he still listened to every word, smiling the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:36.45,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,And the best part - he even brought me flowers as a gift for passing my exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:39.95,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Every girl loves getting flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:43.85,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll dry them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:49.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I want this happiness to last forever.
